						<td valign="top" class="tablefloating" colspan="2">As the game industry continues to grow, knowing where the market is headed is essential in participating in the industry’s growth. This session will assemble key personnel from the game industry’s most successful publishing companies as well as the top online entertainment and media site and ask them to discuss how they are preparing their companies to capitalize on the growing appetite for interactive entertainment. Take a front row seat as a quartet of industry visionaries and decision-makers tell us where they believe this entertainment sector is headed, how they are leveraging their current product and service lineup for future growth, and what areas are ripe for development.&nbsp;</td>
